doi:10.1016/0010-0277(89)90023-1</li>

<li>Cotnoir, Aaron J., 2018, &ldquo;Logical Nihilism&rdquo; in J.
Wyatt, Pederson, and Kellen 2018: 301&ndash;329.
doi:10.1007/978-3-319-98346-2_13</li>

<li>Davidson, Donald, 1973 [1984], &ldquo;Radical
Interpretation&rdquo;, <em>Dialectica</em>, 27(3&ndash;4):
313&ndash;328. Reprinted in his <em>Inquiries into Truth and
