doi:10.1111/j.1746-8361.1973.tb00623.x
doi:10.1093/0199246297.003.0009.</li>

<li>Dicher, Bogdan, 2021, &ldquo;Requiem for Logical Nihilism, or:
Logical Nihilism Annihilated&rdquo;, <em>Synthese</em>, 198(8):
7073&ndash;7096. doi:10.1007/s11229-019-02510-4</li>

<li>Eklund, Matti, 2012, &ldquo;The Multitude View on Logic&rdquo;, in
